ecobee Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























ecobee inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Electrical Equipment
Sub-Industry: Comml & Res Bldg Equip & Sys
ecobee Inc. develops and manufactures thermostats. The Company offers a wide range of thermostats for residential and commercial applications including programmable thermostats that include smartphone applications for programming. ecobee markets its products and services throughout North America and Australia.




Corporate Information
Address:

333 Adelaide Street West
Toronto, ON M5V 1R5
Canada


Phone:
1-877-932-6233


Fax:
1-647-592-7344


Web url:
www.ecobee.com























