ecobee, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 5:01 AM ET
Electronic Equipment, Instruments and Components

Company Overview of ecobee, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ecobee, Inc. manufactures and sells Wi-Fi enabled smart thermostats with remote sensors for residential and commercial applications. The company also offers a mobile application in support to its products through iOS, Android, and BlackBerry platforms. It sells its products through retail stores, professional HVAC contractors, and resellers, as well as its own and other online stores in North America. ecobee, Inc. was formerly known as Avaning Inc. and changed its name to ecobee, Inc. in October 2008. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Toronto, Canada.


250 University AvenueSuite 400Toronto, ON M5H 3E5CanadaFounded in 2007



Phone: 647-428-2220

