History[edit]
Ecobee was founded in 2007.[25] It has been recognized with a number of awards, including the Deloitte Technology Green 15 Award for Canadian green technology companies,[26] and the 2011 AHR Expo Innovation Award in the category of building automation.[27]
Integration[edit]
Ecobee products integrate with: Amazon Alexa, Apple HomeKit, Samsung SmartThings, Wink, Haiku Fans, IFTTT, Logitech Harmony, Vera, and Control4. Ecobee uses an open API[28] for additional integration options.
