EcoBee Inc 
Submitted by Derek on Fri, 12/30/2011 - 14:48






http://www.ecobeeworld.com 








Phone:707.553.6190 


Category InformationGloves, Infection Prevention, Masks, Gloves, Infection Prevention, Masks 


Products from this Manufacturer



 
 



At EcoBee, we do not claim to be perfect however we are taking a positive step toward a more sustainable way of life. It’s undeniable that global warming is already affecting the world we know. The good news is that the know-how to fix this problem and prevent a global environmental disaster exists. As individuals there are many simple steps we can take to cut global warming pollution by making conserving energy a part of our daily routine. For example, each time we choose a compact fluorescent light bulb over an incandescent bulb, we’ll lower our energy bill and keep nearly 700 pounds of carbon dioxide out of the air over the bulb’s lifetime. With our EcoBee products, we’re adopting this simple course of conservation.

















 






